"title": "1075: God, justice of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "1075: god, justice of",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The moral righteousness of God is revealed in his laws and expressed in his judicial acts.  God's commands and judgments meet perfect standards of justice, and his apportioning of punishments and rewards is also perfectly just.  God's justice is impartial.  Special praise is his for vindicating the penitent and the needy who have no human champions. Ultimately, all God's ways will be seen as just and equitable.</p>\n<h2>God's justice displays his righteousness</h2>\n<h3>It conforms to his moral law</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job34:12\">JOB 34:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:4\">DEU 32:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps9:16\">PSA 9:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps11:7\">PSA 11:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph3:5\">ZEP 3:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:2\">ROM 2:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:13\">2TI 2:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev15:3\">REV 15:3</a></p>\n<h3>It is seen in his perfect will</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps99:4\">PSA 99:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps40:8\">PSA 40:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:10\">ISA 53:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:10\">MAT 6:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:39\">MAT 26:39</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:36\">MRK 14:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:42\">LUK 22:42</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:9-Heb10:10\">HEB 10:9–10:10</a></p>\n<h2>God acts with justice</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps33:5-Ps33:15\">PSA 33:5–33:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:33\">NEH 9:33</a></p>\n<h3>God's justice is exercised fairly and equitably</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps9:7-Ps9:8\">PSA 9:7–9:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps96:13\">PSA 96:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps98:9\">PSA 98:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps99:4\">PSA 99:4</a></p>\n<h3>He judges people according to their deeds</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev20:12-Rev20:13\">REV 20:12–20:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod34:6-Exod34:7\">EXO 34:6–34:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps62:12\">PSA 62:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer17:10\">JER 17:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek18:20\">EZK 18:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:27\">MAT 16:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:12\">REV 22:12</a></p>\n<h3>He punishes wickedness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek18:20\">EZK 18:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod34:7\">EXO 34:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:35\">DEU 32:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa59:18\">ISA 59:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa66:24\">ISA 66:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:41-Matt25:46\">MAT 25:41–25:46</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:25\">COL 3:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess1:8-2Thess1:9\">2TH 1:8–1:9</a></p>\n<h3>He rewards righteousness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps58:11\">PSA 58:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa62:11\">ISA 62:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:12\">MAT 5:12</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:23\">LUK 6:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:34-Matt25:40\">MAT 25:34–25:40</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:46\">MAT 25:46</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:7\">ROM 2:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:1-Rom8:2\">ROM 8:1–8:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:8\">2TI 4:8</a></p>\n<h2>God establishes justice</h2>\n<h3>He upholds the cause of the oppressed</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps103:6\">PSA 103:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut10:18\">DEU 10:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps140:12\">PSA 140:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps146:7-Ps146:9\">PSA 146:7–146:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa61:8\">ISA 61:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:52-Luke1:53\">LUK 1:52–1:53</a></p>\n<h3>He vindicates those who have been wronged</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam25:39\">1SA 25:39</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam24:15\">1SA 24:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps135:14\">PSA 135:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:19\">ROM 12:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:35\">DEU 32:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:23\">1PE 2:23</a></p>\n<h3>He is completely impartial</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job34:18-Job34:19\">JOB 34:18–34:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut10:17\">DEU 10:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr19:7\">2CH 19:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:34-Acts10:35\">ACT 10:34–10:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:9\">EPH 6:9</a></p>\n<h2>God's ways in exercising justice</h2>\n<h3>God's justice is not always immediately apparent</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer12:1\">JER 12:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job21:7\">JOB 21:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps73:3-Ps73:14\">PSA 73:3–73:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl7:15\">ECC 7:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab1:2-Hab1:4\">HAB 1:2–1:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal2:17\">MAL 2:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal3:14-Mal3:15\">MAL 3:14–3:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt20:10-Matt20:12\">MAT 20:10–20:12</a></p>\n<h3>God warns before punishing</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr36:15\">2CH 36:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs17:23\">2KI 17:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:29-Neh9:30\">NEH 9:29–9:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer7:13\">JER 7:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah3:4\">JON 3:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:25\">HEB 12:25</a></p>\n<h3>God gives opportunity for people to change their ways</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer18:8-Jer18:10\">JER 18:8–18:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer7:5-Jer7:7\">JER 7:5–7:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek18:25-Ezek18:32\">EZK 18:25–18:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:28-Matt21:32\">MAT 21:28–21:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John1:9\">1JN 1:9</a></p>\n<h2>God's justice is truly equitable</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal6:7-Gal6:8\">GAL 6:7–6:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen18:25\">GEN 18:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num32:23\">NUM 32:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps73:17\">PSA 73:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke16:25\">LUK 16:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:7-Luke18:8\">LUK 18:7–18:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:24-Col3:25\">COL 3:24–3:25</a></p>\n<h2>God's justice is satisfied by the work of Jesus Christ</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:25-Rom3:26\">ROM 3:25–3:26</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:10-Isa53:11\">ISA 53:10–53:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb9:22\">HEB 9:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John1:9\">1JN 1:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:1-1John2:2\">1JN 2:1–2:2</a></p>\n<h2>God's justice will be established in the reign of Jesus Christ</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:31-Matt25:33\">MAT 25:31–25:33</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa9:6-Isa9:7\">ISA 9:6–9:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:31\">ACT 17:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev19:11-Rev19:16\">REV 19:11–19:16</a></p>\n<h3>Heaven and earth will rejoice when God's justice is established</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps96:10-Ps96:13\">PSA 96:10–96:13</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr16:30-1Chr16:33\">1CH 16:30–16:33</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps98:4-Ps98:9\">PSA 98:4–98:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev15:3-Rev15:4\">REV 15:3–15:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev16:5-Rev16:7\">REV 16:5–16:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev19:1-Rev19:2\">REV 19:1–19:2</a></p>\n<h2>God requires people to reflect his justice</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov21:3\">PRO 21:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:15\">LEV 19:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut16:20\">DEU 16:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut24:17\">DEU 24:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs10:9\">1KI 10:9</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr9:8\">2CH 9:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps82:3-Ps82:4\">PSA 82:3–82:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa56:1\">ISA 56:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic6:8\">MIC 6:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech7:9-Zech7:10\">ZEC 7:9–7:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col4:1\">COL 4:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim5:21\">1TI 5:21</a></p>",
